  "description": "Absent-minded Crash Magazine writers went to the pub and left their work on a table in a beer garden. A strong gust of wind has now blown the pages all over town! Help Egghead search for the missing pages so that the next edition of Crash can be put together.<br><br><i>Egghead Goes to Town</i> is the sixth game in the main <i>Egghead</i> series and was created as a perk for backers of the Crash Annual 2018 Kickstarter campaign by Fusion Retro Books. It is a multi flip-screen platform collecting game, with one or two pages to collect per screen. Egghead can climb up ladders or jump across platforms but can't fall too far or he will splatter. There are also fixed-pattern enemies to avoid, often themed to that area of town.",
